title: Op-ed: With world in 'rupture', too many economic roads lead away from Trump and back to China
summary_full: The world is moving back closer to China, and unlike during its ascension to the World Trade Organization, this time it is a move away from the United States.
summary_public: The world is moving back closer to China, and unlike during its ascension to the World Trade Organization, this time it is a move away from the United States.
